OL,4,Ctribute acts on bill following deadly
OL,5,Ccrush
OL,7,FThe O2 Academy Brixton will reopen in
OL,8,FApril, 16 months after a deadly crush
OL,9,Fat the venue.
OL,11,FSecurity guard Gaby Hutchinson, 23,
OL,12,Fand Rebecca Ikumelo, 33, were killed
OL,13,Fwhen fans without tickets tried to
OL,14,Fforce their way into a show by
OL,15,FNigerian artist Asake on December 15
OL,16,F2022.
