OL,7,FThe south London venue faced permanent
OL,8,Fclosure after the Metropolitan Police
OL,9,Furged the council to remove its
OL,10,Flicence but following a two-day
OL,11,Fhearing in September 2023, ` so long
OL,12,Fas it meets "77 extensive and robust
OL,13,Fnew conditions".
OL,15,FIt has now been confirmed the first
OL,16,Fshows at the venue will feature
OL,17,Ftribute acts, rather than famous bands.
