OL,7,FA statement on X said: "O2 Academy
OL,8,FBrixton will reopen on Friday 19 April
OL,9,Fwith Nirvana UK (tribute to Nirvana)
OL,10,Fand The Smyths (tribute to The
OL,11,FSmiths), followed by Friday 26 April
OL,12,Fwith Definitely Mightbe (tribute to
OL,13,FOasis) and UK Food Fighters (tribute
OL,14,Fto Foo Fighters)."
OL,16,FAbout 1,000 people were outside the
OL,17,Fvenue and police found "large-scale
OL,18,Fdisorder" with crowds eventually
OL,19,Fpushing the doors open, according to
OL,20,FGerald Gouriet KC, who represented the
OL,21,FMet at an earlier licensing meeting.
