OL,7,FWhen the doors were breached the crowd
OL,8,Fpoured into the lobby towards the
OL,9,Fauditorium and surged over people who
OL,10,Fhad fallen to the floor.
OL,12,FThe company which owns the Brixton
OL,13,FAcademy, Academy Music Group (AMG),
OL,14,Fsaid it had developed new safety
OL,15,Fmeasures in an effort to have its
OL,16,Flicence restored, including stronger
OL,17,Fdoors, a better queuing system and
OL,18,Fmore secure ticketing.
