OL,7,FAMG said changes to its operating
OL,8,Fpolicies had been developed by
OL,9,F"leading professionals" to prevent a
OL,10,Frepeat of last year's events.
OL,12,FThe venue has spent #1.2 million on
OL,13,Fmaintenance and improvements in 2023,
OL,14,Fdespite being closed, a hearing was
OL,15,Ftold.
OL,17,FFollowing the ruling, Brixton Academy
OL,18,Fsaid it was "immensely grateful" to
OL,19,FLambeth Council and looked forward to
OL,20,Fwelcoming fans back.
